 and intertwined=E2=80=A6Elon is an ex-OpenAI co-founder, is now suing and =
competing against OpenAI, while Larry Ellison who is a known Elon-backer, i=
s teaming up with OpenAI to make it all possible, and Trump is seemingly st=
iff-arming Elon on this deal but elevating him everywhere else. Thankfully,=
 I think all of the gentlemen involved will be A-OK, despite some potential=
 hurt feelings.
