From The White House
It is thus in the national interest to unleash America=E2=80=99s affordable=
 and reliable energy and natural resources. This will restore American pros=
perity =E2=80=94- including for those men and women who have been forgotten=
 by our economy in recent years. It will also rebuild our Nation=E2=80=99s =
