Ten years ago, I was a sophomore at Georgetown and didn=E2=80=99t really kn=
ow what I wanted to do with my life. I remember Packy, who is 8 years older=
 than me, basically sitting me down and saying something to the effect of: =
=E2=80=9Cyou don=E2=80=99t have any excuses, there is some much information=
