et started.=E2=80=9D Since then, I=E2=80=99ve been pretty addicted to podca=
sts and I think they=E2=80=99ve changed the curve of my life.=20
One of the first episodes that really got me hooked was Chris Sacca=E2=80=
=99s first appearance on Tim Ferriss. Here was this Georgetown alumnus, who=
 seemed like we could=E2=80=99ve been friends if we attended school at the =
